    • Method Detail

      • get

        public static <T> T get(ContextPath contextPath,
                        Class<T> returnCls,
                        RequestOptions options,
                        SchemaInfo returnSchemaInfo)
        Returns the json from an HTTP GET of the url built from the contextPath and options. In the case where the returned object is actually a sub-class of T we lookup the sub-class from schemaInfo based on the namespaced type of the return object.
        Type Parameters:
        T - return object type
        Parameters:
        contextPath - context and current path
        returnCls - return class
        options - request options
        returnSchemaInfo - schema to be used for lookup generated class of of the returned object from the namespaced type
        Returns:
        object hydrated from json
